{"id":1651516,"retrievedAt":"2026-03-14T11:44:09.763Z","response":{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":null,"belongs_to_collection":null,"budget":0,"genres":[{"id":99,"name":"Documentary"}],"homepage":"","id":1651516,"imdb_id":null,"origin_country":["FR","US"],"original_language":"en","original_title":"Love Cruising","overview":"A docu-fiction about my trip to the American West Coast (August 2025), where I went in search of car rims that I enjoyed photographing. The sound, which I created myself, is a reading of letters I wrote to Alain.e, who stayed behind in Brittany, describing the cars I encountered, accompanied by Olga, the BMW I was driving. It's an affectionate reference to Chantal Akerman's *News From Home*. The short film opens with a series of archival images of a Virginia Woolf house that I photographed (2015). Like Alain.e, my van is my nomadic haven; it's an ironic wink. The twist lies in the VW painted by Virginia Woolf on one of her chairs, the meaning of which I subvert. I love humor, however, I have no irony whatsoever about my taste for car tuning, and queer tuning.","popularity":0.0071,"poster_path":null,"production_companies":[],"production_countries":[],"release_date":"2024-12-13","revenue":0,"runtime":14,"spoken_languages":[{"english_name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English"},{"english_name":"French","iso_639_1":"fr","name":"Français"}],"status":"Released","tagline":"","title":"Love Cruising","video":false,"vote_average":0,"vote_count":0,"alternative_titles":{"titles":[{"iso_3166_1":"FR","title":"Mon Amérique à Moi C'est Toi","type":""}]},"credits":{"cast":[{"adult":false,"gender":0,"id":6069796,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Juliana Dorso","original_name":"Juliana Dorso","popularity":0.0071,"profile_path":null,"cast_id":1,"character":"Juliana Dorso","credit_id":"69b4930204a599bcec7318ae","order":0}],"crew":[{"adult":false,"gender":0,"id":6069796,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Juliana Dorso","original_name":"Juliana Dorso","